        "id": 1141499
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-01-18T05:56:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "since you\u0027ve mentioned effective limit on max batch size, perhaps mention limit of new commits per single ref?\nhttps://cs.chromium.org/chromium/infra/go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/scheduler/appengine/task/gitiles/gitiles.go?q\u003dscheduler+gitiles.go\u0026sq\u003dpackage:chromium\u0026g\u003d0\u0026l\u003d58",
      "revId": "0469239ffe948c60413cf6e24559ff4fde8371c1",
