      "writtenOn": "2019-01-18T17:22:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "you did, which means comment there is insufficient :(\n\nWhen a single ref goes from R_m to R_n, scheduler will only query gitiles for at most defaultMaxCommitsPerRefUpdate, ignoring everything else (ie from R_m to R_(n-50)\n\nsee https://cs.chromium.org/chromium/infra/go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/scheduler/appengine/task/gitiles/gitiles.go?q\u003dscheduler+gitiles.go\u0026sq\u003dpackage:chromium\u0026g\u003d0\u0026l\u003d229",
